Load Dataset to Power BI Desktop 9
  • Click on the  red button    above to download  the Zip file  AirData.xlsx data file. It Contains the data that we are using to build the dashboard.
  • Load the dataset to Power BI desktop using the outline from the previous step. Follow the GIF below:

To achieve optimum performance and avoid creating additional calculated columns in PBI, these columns were added on the excel file:

  1. MonthYear  =  CONCAT([@MonthName]," ",[@year])
  2. NonCarrierCausedDelay  =  SUM([@carrier_ct], [@weather_ct], [@nas_ct])

Concatenate function:

https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/office/concatenate-function-8f8ae884-2ca8-4f7a-b093-75d702bea31d
